reviewText: Watched this on the TV and liked the message so much I ordered the DVD for our youth program at Harris Chapel UMC. While not strictly a "Christian" film, it is a fun, science fictional non-preachy, way to share our christian faith that young (and older) people will enjoy. Bob Jernigan, Pastor. [...]

Though the plot was quite complex and forcing characters to spend a little too much time explaining, I did enjoy the movie's premise and sincere acting.  The verse: what profits a man who gains the world but loses his soul? kept going through my mind.  See it and find out why.
